|               |           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                             |
|               |             ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@1 AS Int64) as id, 1 - distance@2 as score, answer@0 as answer]                                                               |
|               |               RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(10), input_partitions=1                                                                                      |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                       |
